{"tid":1831104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不太巧，本赛季西班牙人西甲共赢3场武磊均未登场","createTime":"2020-01-20T06:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T15:57:26.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd48707997bfba910ddc6a9d7d5eb93368c14165","tid":1831104,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"1月20日讯 在昨天的一场西甲联赛中，副班长西班牙人队2-1客场击败了比利亚雷亚尔，终结了9轮不胜。本赛季至今，西班牙人共赢下了3场西甲联赛，而中国球员武磊在这些比赛中均未登场。<br />\n<br />\n在本赛季的武磊未登场的4轮比赛中，西班牙人取得3胜1平保持不败，而在武磊登场的16轮比赛中，西班牙人则是4平12负战绩糟糕。<br />\n<br />\n武磊本赛季在10场西甲比赛中担任替补，在球队取得领先的情况下，作为前锋的他很难拿到上场机会。"},{"pid":"bfc3e599de8c13998945a8a95bf1c5f3a5d76cd1","tid":1831104,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇佢就贏"},{"pid":"e2ba12cc9b1e228a058bc19511cb11ad55c18a26","tid":1831104,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfc3e599de8c13998945a8a95bf1c5f3a5d76cd1","tid":1831104,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇佢就贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir"},{"pid":"75f6b03d4ca90079c94cc2bb2a401533d942ac10","tid":1831104,"uid":41575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"若要護級 必先無武磊"}]}